 sauce","1 tsp sesame oil","20 g peanut oil","½ - 1 tsp salt, to taste"]},{"title":"Chicken","content":["500 g water","500 g chicken tenderloins (see Tips)","salt, to season","ground black pepper, to season"]},{"title":"Salad","content":["100 g rice vermicelli noodles","boiling water, for soaking","170 g carrot, peeled and cut into pieces (approx. 5 cm)","½ Chinese cabbage, cut into halves lengthways, then cut into thin slices crossways","2 spring onions\/shallots, trimmed and cut into thin slices on a diagonal","130 g red capsicum, trimmed and cut into thin strips","70 g snow peas, cut into thin strips","2 sprigs fresh mint, leaves only","4 sprigs fresh coriander, leaves only","2 tbsp roasted salted peanuts, roughly chopped, for garnishing","1 tsp sesame seeds, toasted (optional)","1 lime, cut into wedges, to serve"]}],"id":"r138489","imageLink":"https:\/\/2.bp.blogspot.com\/-x5zKMNm2smg\/XZQxEXNcjkI\/AAAAAAAAcrY\/D37TPfPNVd0RK43zhx063WN6VlUbX_MYACLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_l9hNhTZ-ffSemoLN.png","title":"Asian chicken noodle salad","publishedAt":"2017-03-19T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"23 g","fat":"15.2 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"32 g","calories":"1541 kJ \/ 367 kcal"},"usefulItems":"bowl, plastic wrap, large bowl, thermal serving bowl or other large bowl, serving plates, refrigerator","hintsAndTricks":["Chicken breasts can be used as a substitute for tenderloins in this recipe. Simply cut 500 g chicken breasts into halves lengthways and steam <strong>14-16 min\/Varoma\/speed 1<\/strong> or until chicken is cooked through.","Salad can be made ahead of time (through step 6), then add dressing just before serving. Store dressing and salad in the refrigerator until ready to serve."],"basicInfo":["easy","20m","45m","6 portions"]}